   BUFFALO, N.Y. -- Delaware North Cos. and LSG Lufthansa
Service G.m.b.H., part of Lufthansa German Airlines, said in
a joint announcement that LSG will acquire Dairy Farm
Catering Group, the Hong Kong-based in-flight food-service
