<LP>
   QUALITY SYSTEMS Inc. (Tustin, Calif.) -- Sy Rubenstein, 51
years old, the company's chief operating officer, was named
president, succeeding Sheldon Razin, 52, who remains chairman
and chief executive officer. The post of chief operating
officer has been eliminated. Quality Systems sells
computerized information processing systems to medical and
dental group practices.
