There are $34.06 million 6 1/8% term bonds priced at 84.22 to
yield 7.45% in 2020. The bonds are rated single-A by Moody's
and single-A-minus by S&amp;P.
   Massachusetts Housing Finance Authority -- $150.9 million
single-family mortgage revenue bonds, Series 13, due June 1,
and Dec. 1, 2014 and 2023, Series 14, due 2014 and Series 15,
due 1991-2005, priced by a PaineWebber Inc. group to yield
from 6.10% in 1991 to 7.95% in 2023. In Series 13 there are
