$1.33 billion of insurance policies and annuities. And, while
the amount of redemptions wasn't reported for the latest
quarter, First Executive's assets tumbled $1.53 billion in
the latest quarter, which may in part reflect policies being
turned in. Assets totaled $16.47 billion at June 30, down
from $18 billion at March 31 and $18.7 billion at June 30,
1989.
